title: Shut Up, Evil Dragon! I don’t want to raise a child with you anymore
description: Shut Up, Evil Dragon! I don’t want to raise a child with you anymore After being defeated and captured, the dragon slayer Leon became a captive of the Silver Dragon Queen. With the awareness of death, he used forbidden magic to curse the queen, but unexpectedly, the queen lost control. He thought that this would make the queen live with shame for the rest of her life, and it would be worthy of the dragon slayer’s mission. But two years later, when Leon opened his eyes, next to him was a little dragon girl with a tail… 闭嘴恶龙我不想再跟你带孩子了 Shut Up, Evil Dragon! I don’t want to raise a child with you anymore
alternative_titles: 闭嘴恶龙我不想再跟你带孩子了
